- License: BSD-3-Clause
- Copyright: © 2000-2009 Josh Coalson, © 2011-2024 Xiph.Org Foundation
- Homepage: https://xiph.org/flac/
- How we ship it: source-compiled inside JUCE.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
