LIBRARIES NOT YET INTEGRATED

The following are referenced by feature plans but are NOT currently
bundled or linked in shipping builds:

- libsamplerate (BSD-2-Clause) - high-quality sample rate conversion
- FFTW or Kiss FFT - FFT for spectrum analyzer (we currently use
  juce::dsp::FFT, no extra dependency)
- libebur128 (MIT) - EBU R128 loudness metering
- RNNoise (BSD-3-Clause) - noise suppression
- Rubber Band Library (GPL v2+) - pitch/time stretching
- Opus (BSD-3-Clause) - Opus codec

All listed/planned licenses are compatible with GPL v3.

